These are Puzzles for 5x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: electronic, rock
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, writer
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, garlic
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, skiing
1. the writer is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person eating garlic is on the far left##1
3. the fan of electronic is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is skiing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Beverage   | juice     | lemonade     |
| Music-Genre   | rock     | electronic |
| Job   | designer | writer  |
| Food           | garlic    | cabbage |
| Sport         | skiing   | golf       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda
The people have 2 different jobs:  manager, scientist
House: victorian, cape-cod
The people have 2 different hobbies: gardening, fishing
City: edinburgh, venice
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the victorian house is the manager##1
3. the victorian house is in an even position##4
4. the scientist is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | almond-milk |
| Job           | scientist  | manager     |
| House   | cape-cod       | victorian      |
| Hobby           | gardening        | fishing      |
| City         | venice | edinburgh     |

