.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: reggae, punk
The people have 2 different jobs:  doctor, dressmaker
City: rome, berlin
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, august
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, skateboard
1. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
3. the fan of punk is in an odd position##4
4. the dressmaker is the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Music-Genre         | punk     | reggae    |
| Job           | doctor     | dressmaker |
| City   | berlin    | rome   |
| Birthday         | april | august   |
| Transport     | helicopter | skateboard |

