.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-4::.
There 2 different types of food: cranberry, kiwi
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, roller
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate
2 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, skateboarding
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
2. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person playing scrabble is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |
| Food          | kiwi     | cranberry     |
| Transport   | helicopter   | roller        |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate      | almond-milk         |
| Game   | scrabble | backgammon       |
| Sport         | cycling  | skateboarding |

