.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-6::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: lavender, blue
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, musician
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: lily, bellflower
2 different pets are kept: hamster, rabbit
City: liverpool, new-york
1. the owner of the hamster is in an odd position##4
2. the fisherman is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
3. the person who likes lavender is the fisherman##1
4. the musician is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Color      | blue        | lavender     |
| Job           | musician   | fisherman |
| Flower   | bellflower     | lily    |
| Pet           | hamster    | rabbit    |
| City         | liverpool | new-york   |

