.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-7::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, bellflower
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, golf
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, romance
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, rock
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, reading
1. the fan of rock is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is in an even position##4
3. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Flower      | amaryllis     | bellflower     |
| Sport          | soccer | golf |
| Movie-Genre   | romance  | adventure  |
| Music-Genre   | disco    | rock       |
| Hobby     | reading      | magic-tricks     |

