.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-8::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: superhero, horror
2 different games are played: backgammon, poker
House: gothic-revival, victorian
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, rat
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, taxi
1. the owner of the rabbit is in an even position##4
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
3. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the gothic-revival house is the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Movie-Genre         | horror  | superhero |
| Game           | poker   | backgammon  |
| House   | victorian | gothic-revival  |
| Pet           | rat     | rabbit      |
| Transport     | taxi    | subway      |

