2. the turkish is on the left of the french##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |
| Beverage      | fanta    | tea         |
| City           | liverpool | miami |
| Food   | kiwi  | cauliflower       |
| Nationality           | turkish     | french  |
| Transport     | ship     | van         |

