.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, tea
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, japanese
2 different pets are kept: ferret, hedgehog
2 different games are played: snooker, mah-jongg
There are 2 different favourite colors: ebony, blood-red
1. the person playing mah-jongg is the australian##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4
4. the australian is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage      | tea      | milk     |
| Nationality   | japanese    | australian  |
| Pet           | ferret   | hedgehog |
| Game         | snooker | mah-jongg |
| Color     | ebony     | blood-red     |

 